<h2 style="margin-bottom: -14px">Android SMS Backup and Donation</h2>
<p><small>
Version: 1.0.1<br/>
Author: Tao Chen </small></p>
<p>Automatically backs up your SMS to Gmail and donates your sent messages for research. Our project aims to collect SMS messages and build a public corpus for research. Our software is a modified version of SMS Backup. Generally, it has the same appearance and function as the original software. The only difference is we  add a module to generate a draft email which contains  messages for donation. </p>

<h3>Information</h3>
<p>Please visit the <a href="%3$s">User Guide</a> for more information and check
 <a href="%4$s">Android Market</a> for updates.</p>

